spec.name: Ettedgui Synagogue
spec.description:
🔻 Architect: Georges Buan
🔻 Dates: 1935
🔻 Current Status: Museum
🔻 Description: This synagogue was initiated by a Jewish Family from Toudgha who came to Casablanca at the end of the 19th century. This was the second synagogue they built in the Medina.
